  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/40f295e894355424f377ad72b3170e65.poster.avif?t=1577182124\" width=640 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/40f295e894355424f377ad72b3170e65.webm?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/40f295e894355424f377ad72b3170e65.mp4?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hit the snow! <br><br>Whether you enjoy skiing, the thrill of barrelling down an ice track in a bobsleigh or sled, or calmly sliding the stones across the ice in curling – you can have it all here.<br><br>Win tournaments and master challenges in six tense disciplines. Play by yourself or with up to four players at your home – no runny nose after every competition!<br><br>Features<br>- 6 tense disciplines:<br>- Ski jumping<br>- Slalom skiing<br>- Downhill skiing<br>- Bobsledding<br>- Sledding<br>- Curling<br>- Local multiplayer for 2 to 4 players<br>- Modern graphics and classic controls<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/ce08afff678d577bf1716e2e7bcf0a2c.poster.avif?t=1577182124\" width=640 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/ce08afff678d577bf1716e2e7bcf0a2c.webm?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/ce08afff678d577bf1716e2e7bcf0a2c.mp4?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/40f295e894355424f377ad72b3170e65.poster.avif?t=1577182124\" width=640 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/40f295e894355424f377ad72b3170e65.webm?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/40f295e894355424f377ad72b3170e65.mp4?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hit the snow! <br><br>Whether you enjoy skiing, the thrill of barrelling down an ice track in a bobsleigh or sled, or calmly sliding the stones across the ice in curling – you can have it all here.<br><br>Win tournaments and master challenges in six tense disciplines. Play by yourself or with up to four players at your home – no runny nose after every competition!<br><br>Features<br>- 6 tense disciplines:<br>- Ski jumping<br>- Slalom skiing<br>- Downhill skiing<br>- Bobsledding<br>- Sledding<br>- Curling<br>- Local multiplayer for 2 to 4 players<br>- Modern graphics and classic controls<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/ce08afff678d577bf1716e2e7bcf0a2c.poster.avif?t=1577182124\" width=640 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/ce08afff678d577bf1716e2e7bcf0a2c.webm?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998530/extras/ce08afff678d577bf1716e2e7bcf0a2c.mp4?t=1577182124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
